A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E6%AA%A2%E6%B8%AC%E9%80%B2%E5%BA%A6%E5%A4%A7%E8%90%BD%E5%BE%8C-%E5%BC%B5%E7%AB%B9%E5%90%9B%E6%8B%92%E5%9B%9E%E6%87%89-%E9%86%AB%E7%AE%A1%E5%B1%80-%E6%AF%8F%E6%97%A5%E6%94%B6-3-%E8%90%AC%E6%A8%A3%E6%9C%AC-%E9%80%90%E6%AD%A5%E5%81%9A%E7%B7%8A/</a><br />\n<br />\n《立場》早前刊出調查報道，指由於政府農曆新年前突然公布，食肆由初七（18 日）起放寬晚市，學校亦恢復半日面授課堂，但要求職員定期檢測，令大批市民急急測試，致檢測服務瀕爆煲。多名上周「交樽仔」到指定收集點的市民，至今逾一周仍未收到結果，而政府的電子檢測紀錄網站，並無相關樣本的紀錄。有查詢熱線的職員承認，檢測結果嚴重滯後，「15、16號（初四及初五）交嘅都未有結果」，換言之至今已滯後 9 日。（見另稿）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n9日都無result，即係中完，病好，再中都夠時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54d6dab497d4175c037f8eace7b71bf2d530c2f8","tid":2421442,"uid":122275,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T13:42:03.000Z","msg":"重要野政府唔會做"},{"pid":"1df9dfada8c6f4d56f9b83704f5044a1e0ffbd78","tid":2421442,"uid":229436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T13:48:59.000Z","msg":"急咩姐下年再話你知有無中"},{"pid":"805197b7a87ebc4a8331f88084d9f255b49759b8","tid":2421442,"uid":294121,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T13:50:01.000Z","msg":"驗唔哂仲係到玩封區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5acea26c1f1b2d7eef597466dffa10c4e9fbdf34","tid":2421442,"uid":51583,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T13:50:50.000Z","msg":"再嘈減你資源丫拿"},{"pid":"1cf9de5e39986b4500fa92420af1eef99ce7f52a","tid":2421442,"uid":51583,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"805197b7a87ebc4a8331f88084d9f255b49759b8","tid":2421442,"uid":294121,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T13:50:01.000Z","msg":"驗唔哂仲係到玩封區<img src=\"/as